name: Demo Flight
location_str: Launch Area 96B @ Jiuquan Satellite Launch Center, CHN
description: First test launch of LandSpace’s ZQ-3 rocket, with a dummy payload. The rocket’s 1st stage will attempt to land on a landing pad about 300 km downrange of the launch site.
rocket_fact: Ion thrusters used on satellites produce about as much force as the weight of a single sheet of paper.
